Repository contains an implementation of multiple interface (MIF)
provisioning domain (PvD) support (discussed by IETF MIF WG).

Included are:
- doc      - PvD architecture description -- start here!
- radvd    - modified radvd server which includes support for
		     PvD container option (for routers)
- pvdman   - MIF PvD manager for client hosts
- api      - API for client applications (in C) that will be PvD aware
- testapps - several PvD aware applications for testing MIF functionality
- demos    - demos that describe and demonstrate MIF functionality
